content:
Outline a Typeform that uses logic to onboard a radio show host at a community radio station to gather the following information:

First Name
Last Name
Personal Email
Would you like a Radio Kingston Email?
If yes what is your desired Radio Kingston Email Address
Will you use your new Radio Kingston Email as your best method of contacting you?
Phone Number
Address
City
State
Zip Code
T-Shirt Size
Hoodie Size
Onboarding Documents 1, 2, 3
Show Name
Show Start Date
Resource Page Information
